<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.8.2">
<l>paḷḷi yāvatu pāṟka ṭalaraṅ kami raṅkavaṉ pēymulai</l>
<l>piḷḷai yāyuyi ruṇṭa ventaipi rāṉa vaṉperu kumiṭam</l>
<l>veḷḷi yāṉkari yāṉma ṇiniṟa vaṇṇa</l>
<l>ṉeṉṟeṇṇi nāṭoṟum</l>
<l>teḷḷi yārvaṇaṅ kumma laitiru vēṅka ṭamaṭai neñcamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] heart, take refuge at Tiruvēṅkaṭam, the mountain</l>
<l rend="indent">where wise men worship every day,</l>
<l>Meditating and saying, “The white one, the dark one, the jewel-hued one,”</l>
<l>The place where the lord prospers, our father</l>
<l rend="indent">who as a babe consumed the demoness’ life at her breast,</l>
<l>The compassionate one [for whom] the Sea of Milk</l>
<l rend="indent">and Araṅkam become his bed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
